<quantity box="[355,403,328,345]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="862" unit="m" value="0.2">0.2 m</quantity>
tall; leaf margins entire, sinuate to weakly lobed; inflorescence with up to ca. 4 flowers.............. 10. 
